---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import GuideNav from "../components/GuideNav.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  variant="home"
  title="First-time China visitor guide — Shanghai"
  description="Practical English guide for first-time visitors to China, first city Shanghai: payments, metro & taxis, and high-speed rail."
>
  <GuideNav slot="nav" currentPath={Astro.url.pathname} />
  <article class="chapter">
    <h1>First-time China visitor guide</h1>
    <p>
      <strong>First city: Shanghai.</strong> English static guide: <strong>pay → move → travel farther</strong>,
      with one on-page branch for <strong>Shanghai</strong> local transport (metro-first vs taxi, bus
      &amp; ride-hail). Product spec: <code>docs/DESIGN-SPEC.md</code> · URL model:{" "}
      <code>docs/URL-STRATEGY.md</code>. Verify apps and rules at official sources before you travel.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Start here:</strong>
      <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}before-land/`}>Before you land</a> (checklist and early connectivity
      callouts).
    </p>
    <section class="activation-callout" aria-label="Task onboarding entry">
      <p class="activation-kicker">NEW · TASK ONBOARDING</p>
      <h2>Use the 72-hour activation flow</h2>
      <p>
        Not a guide to read end-to-end. This is a progression board that unlocks capability step by step:
        payments, mobility, and connectivity.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a class="activation-link" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}onboarding/`}>Open onboarding system</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
  <style>
    .activation-callout {
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem 1rem;
      border: 2px solid var(--text);
      background: var(--bg-elevated);
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 color-mix(in srgb, var(--text) 80%, transparent);
    }
    .activation-kicker {
      margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .activation-callout h2 {
      margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
      font-size: 1.22rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .activation-callout p {
      margin: 0.4rem 0 0;
    }
    .activation-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 2.6rem;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.9rem;
      border: 2px solid var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 12%, var(--bg-elevated));
    }
    .activation-link:hover {
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 22%, var(--bg-elevated));
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
